    {
      "text": "func parseHeading(line string) (heading, bool) {\n\thashCount := 0\n\tfor i := 0; i \u003c len(line) \u0026\u0026 i \u003c 7; i++ {\n\t\tif line[i] == '#' {\n\t\t\thashCount++\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tbreak\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tif hashCount \u003e 0 \u0026\u0026 hashCount \u003c= 6 \u0026\u0026 len(line) \u003e hashCount \u0026\u0026 line[hashCount] == ' ' {\n\t\treturn heading{depth: hashCount, title: strings.TrimSpace(line[hashCount+1:])}, true\n\t}\n\treturn heading{}, false\n}",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/chunk/markdown.go \u003e function parseHeading\n\nfunc parseHeading(line string) (heading, bool) {\n\thashCount := 0\n\tfor i := 0; i \u003c len(line) \u0026\u0026 i \u003c 7; i++ {\n\t\tif line[i] == '#' {\n\t\t\thashCount++\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tbreak\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tif hashCount \u003e 0 \u0026\u0026 hashCount \u003c= 6 \u0026\u0026 len(line) \u003e hashCount \u0026\u0026 line[hashCount] == ' ' {\n\t\treturn heading{depth: hashCount, title: strings.TrimSpace(line[hashCount+1:])}, true\n\t}\n\treturn heading{}, false\n}",
      "headingContext": "internal/chunk/markdown.go \u003e function parseHeading",
      "startLine": 41,
